# Mini GPT From Scratch

This repository documents my journey of building a Transformer-based language model from scratch.

The goal is to understand every component instead of treating AI as a black box.

Progress

- [x] Basic Tokenizer
- [ ] Vocabulary
- [ ] Token IDs
- [ ] Embeddings
- [ ] Self Attention
- [ ] Multi Head Attention
- [ ] Feed Forward Network
- [ ] Layer Normalization
- [ ] Transformer Block
- [ ] Training
- [ ] Text Generation